title: Jim Jones Interview and more!
itunes:title: Jim Jones Interview and more!
description:
Jim Jones pulled up on the Breakfast Club to talk about Tekashi 69 ...or not. He also spoke about his music and his "Saucey" business with Alex Todd. Angela Yee gave a few callers relationship advice and Charlamagne gave two Florida residents Donkey of the Day for unlawfully taking an alligator to be their drinking buddy.
